title: 110: Digging Deep with a Paleontologist | Ear Biscuits Ep. 110
description:
Rhett & Link sit down with Dr. Emily Lindsey, a paleontologist working at the La Brea Tar Pits, to discuss that dig site, how Rhett would do in the field, her continuing work on Ice Age animals, and more on this week's Ear Biscuits.
